      "text": "は～～い！　そんなの簡単です！",
      "startTime": 219.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "腕と腰の間の三角形を意識して\nキレイな三角を作って",
      "startTime": 225.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "キレイな三角……こうですか？",
      "startTime": 227.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いいよ\nさすがだな、ダンスで鍛えているから画になるよ",
      "startTime": 232.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr024.m4a",
      "text": "こころはLizNoirですから！\nさらに、パリコレ風ターンなんかも決めちゃいます！",
      "startTime": 239.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "それはちょっとネタっぽいな",
      "startTime": 243.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr025.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですよ、アイドルには親しみやすさも\n必要なんです！",
      "startTime": 248.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr026.m4a",
      "text": "決めポーズで、キラキラアイドルスマイル！",
      "startTime": 250.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いいな\n新しいLizNoirって感じだ",
      "startTime": 256.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr027.m4a",
      "text": "ですよね！\n最近はMCで莉央さんも葵さんも笑ってますし",
      "startTime": 260.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
