      "text": "ああ、LizNoirは変わったよ\nもちろん、いい意味で",
      "startTime": 267.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr028.m4a",
      "text": "こころと愛ちゃんが加入して\n海外遠征した成果ですよ～",
      "startTime": 271.8666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
