      "text": "そうか、君達が新しいLizNoirの魅力を\n引き出したのか。大したものだよ",
      "startTime": 278.46666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr029.m4a",
      "text": "それに気が付くとは、なかなか見る目が――\nあれ？　いつの間にか私、心を許しつつある……？",
      "startTime": 285.6666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr030.m4a",
      "text": "さてはこころを褒め殺して、懐柔するつもりですね～？\n油断も隙もありません！",
      "startTime": 296.14451104030013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh024.m4a",
      "text": "（一筋縄ではいかないな……）\n（でも、可能性を感じさせる子だ……）",
      "startTime": 301.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
